metadata.name: Summer Alley
metadata.description:
Thanks for taking a look.
This is a photo of a typical Japanese alleyway, taken in Okayama Prefecture at dusk.
In addition, it has a fantastic finish.
This is truly a magnificent piece of work.

「氷」means ice.
The light and everything else is a fantastic effect.

By the way, I'm a photographer who publishes a book all over Japan called "Fantasy Flower World"!
I'm proud to say that I'm one of the most promising photographers in Japan right now.

Photo Date
July 16, 2020

I hope you will like this special work.
